@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bgdoez(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin((0.79 + wp.sin(v0 + 0.07)))
    v2 = (tmp / wp.sin(0.40))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.50 + v0 + 0.73) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.03)) * ((v2 + 0.56 - tmp + 0.91) * tmp))
    v1 = (wp.cos(v1) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
